  "description": "The Time Slice CHOP outputs a time slice of samples. It is used to generate smooth in-betweens when TouchDesigner cannot cook/draw fast enough and keep up with the animation's frames per second. When you send it to a Record CHOP or Gesture CHOP, you will see the channels recorded and playing back more smoothly.",
  "summary": "The Time Slice CHOP outputs a time slice of samples. It is used to generate smooth in-betweens when TouchDesigner cannot cook/draw fast enough and keep up with the animation's frames per second. When ",
